Developer Terms of Use
des:
In this game, you tell Alexa what choices to make as you explore the options in the game.

To start, just say "Alexa, open Get Me Out Of Here" or "Alexa, launch Get Me Out Of Here" to start a game".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop".
